# Bundled Tauri sidecars live here.
#
# Build the AXL Go binary per-target and drop it as:
#   axl-aarch64-apple-darwin
#   axl-x86_64-apple-darwin
#   axl-x86_64-pc-windows-msvc.exe
#   axl-x86_64-unknown-linux-gnu
#
# Same naming convention for 0g-storage-client-<target>. Tauri's
# `externalBin` and the sidecar lifecycle code in `src-tauri/src/` will
# reference these files; they are intentionally not committed.
